street because he's never sure.

01:07:14.970 --> 01:07:16.366
What do you think?

01:07:16.366 --> 01:07:21.159
AUDIENCE: I actually think that
there's a much larger fraction

01:07:21.159 --> 01:07:22.992
where it's exactly the
