01:17:30.420 --> 01:17:31.350
Ready.

01:17:31.350 --> 01:17:35.150
Three, two, one.

01:17:35.150 --> 01:17:35.650
All right.

01:17:35.650 --> 01:17:38.880
So we have, I'd say,
a majority of nos.

01:17:38.880 --> 01:17:40.550
And can somebody say why not?

01:17:40.550 --> 01:17:43.540
AUDIENCE: You can't really
see the established mutation.

